        <custodhist id="ref4">
            <head>Provenance</head>
            <p>The Irving Weissman Photograph Collection was donated by Mr. Weissman to the Abraham Lincoln Brigade Archives, then held at Brandeis University, in 1994. This collection came to New York University in January 2001 as part of the original acquisition of Abraham Lincoln Brigade Archives collections, formerly housed at Brandeis University. The images in the Weissman Photograph Collection were separated from the Weissman manuscript material at the time of processing.</p>
        </custodhist>
        <accessrestrict id="ref5">
